    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A surface analysis technique which measures the elastically scattered ion created when a primary ion beam is directed at the sample surface. The kinetic energy of the reflected primary ion depends on the mass of the surface atom involved in scattering, thus revealing information about the sample surface.   </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
